---
// Offline chat — flagship design preview. Mirrors docs/design/chat-spec.md:
// model chip + live tok/s ticker, streaming bubble, collapsible reasoning,
// code well with copy, star typing indicator, trust mark, composer.
import StarGlyph from '../StarGlyph.astro';
---

<div class="mk-appbar">
  <span class="mk-back">‹</span>
  <span class="mk-chip">Llama-3.2-1B <span aria-hidden="true">▾</span></span>
  <span class="mk-spacer"></span>
  <span class="mk-tokps">38.6 tok/s</span>
  <span class="mk-more" aria-hidden="true">⋮</span>
</div>

<div class="mk-body">
  <div class="mk-bubble user">Explain a stack in one line, then show a Dart example.</div>

  <div class="mk-reason">
    <span class="caret" aria-hidden="true">▸</span>
    <span>Reasoning (4s)</span>
  </div>

  <div class="mk-bubble bot">
    A stack is a last-in, first-out collection: the last item you push is the first you pop.
    <div class="mk-code">
      <div class="mk-code-head">
        <span>dart</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">⧉ copy</span>
      </div>
      <pre><span class="tok-key">final</span> stack = &lt;<span class="tok-key">int</span>&gt;[];
stack.<span class="tok-str">add</span>(1);   <span class="tok-str">// push</span>
stack.<span class="tok-str">removeLast</span>(); <span class="tok-str">// pop</span></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="mk-meta"><span>just now</span><span class="mk-dot">·</span><span>38.6 tok/s</span></div>

  <div class="mk-typing" aria-hidden="true">
    <StarGlyph class="mk-star" />
    <StarGlyph class="mk-star" />
    <StarGlyph class="mk-star" />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mk-trust">
  <StarGlyph class="mk-star" />
  <span>Runs 100% on your device</span>
</div>

<div class="mk-composer">
  <svg class="mk-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h10"/></svg>
  <span class="mk-field">Message Dhruva…</span>
  <span class="mk-send"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 3l18 9-18 9 4-9-4-9z"/></svg></span>
</div>
